      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Blue, Round, and Cute",
        "Client": "Whimsical Researcher",
        "Description": "You there! Tell me, don\u0027t you\r\nthink Arzuros are the cutest!?\r\nFuzzy blue fur, a soft tubby\r\nbelly; what I wouldn\u0027t give to\r\nhug \u0027em! Sooo, can you capture\r\none for m\u2014 Whaddya mean,\r\n\u0022only if I promise not to hug it?\u0022",
        "Target": "Capture an Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, time expires,\r\nor capture target slain"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Bleu, rond, mignon",
        "Client": "Chercheur capricieux",
        "Description": "Eh, toi l\u00E0-bas ! Tu trouves\r\npas que les Arzuros sont trop\r\nmignons avec leur fourrure\r\nbleue et leur petit ventre ?\r\nJe voudrais tellement en\r\nserrer un dans mes bras...\r\nTu voudrais m\u0027aider ?",
        "Target": "Capturer un Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9\r\nCible tu\u00E9e"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Blu, tondi e carini",
        "Client": "Ricercatore stravagante",
        "Description": "Ehi! Non pensi che gli Arzuros\r\nsiano carinissimi? Quel pelo\r\nblu e quella pancia morbida.\r\nCome vorrei abbracciarne uno!\r\nNon \u00E8 cheee, ehm, potresti\r\ncatturarne uno... Eh? Solo se\r\nprometto di non abbracciarlo?!",
        "Target": "Cattura un Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero, tempo scaduto\r\no mostro da catturare ucciso"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Blau, rund und s\u00FC\u00DF",
        "Client": "Schrulliger Forscher",
        "Description": "Du da! Sind Arzuros nicht das\r\nS\u00FC\u00DFeste auf der ganzen Welt?!\r\nWeiches blaues Fell, ein ku-\r\ngelrunder Bauch; einfach zum\r\nKnuddeln! F\u00E4ngst du einen f\u00FCr\r\nmi-- ... Wie? Ich muss schw\u00F6-\r\nren, ihn nicht zu knuddeln?",
